Package edu.uoregon.autograder.util

Class Summary
GraderRunner This class manages a queue of Graders, executing them sequentially in a separate thread from the servlet so that the servlet can continue to process new grading requests and serve status pages for queued or finished requests.
ShellAccess This class is used statically to execute a command at the shell and capture the stdout and stderr from that command execution.
ShellOutputError A simple class to hold the results (stdout and stderr) of executing a shell command.
